<h3>Steps to Run the Command<h3>
<ol>
<li>Download Ollama from the browser</li>
<li>Download gemma:2b model using terminal (command: ollama pull gemma:2b)</li>
<li>install all the requirements from the requirements.txt file (command: pip install -r requirements.txt)</li>
<li>Run the current file using Streamlit (command: streamlit run current_file_name.py)</li>
</ol>
